<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Eger</head><p>Der Rat dankt für die Unterstützung seiner Gesandtschaft nach Elbogen. Im beigefügten Zettel bittet der Rat um Neuigkeiten zu den Geschehnissen in Böhmen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_237" id="117v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_237_r1l23">Den von Eger </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_237_r1l24"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe wır nehſt ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> vnd ʒum </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l25"><expan>Ellmpog<ex>en</ex></expan> geſant hetten / wol fürbracht vnd geſagt / wıe Jr Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l26">dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vnd auch eẅr <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> gelıhen vnd ʒugeſchıkt vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l27">vnd guten <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in den ſachen beweıſet habt / Des wır <expan>eẅer<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l28"><expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſſ <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd vmb eẅch vnd dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l29"><expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ʒuuerſchulde<ex>n</ex></expan> wo das an vns gelangt Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l30"><expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_237_r1l31"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> Judıca </ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><pb facs="#facs_238" id="118r"/>
<l> Cettula <expan>int<ex>er</ex>cluſa</expan> </l>
<ab facs="#facs_237_line_1577190999379_306"/>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l1">Auch <expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> / Ob Jr von den <expan>lawffe<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu Beheim ıcht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l2">meͣr hettet dıe vns <expan>ʒuuerſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> ſeın daʒ Jr vns bey <expan>dıſ<ex>em</ex></expan> <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> ın <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l3"><expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet als vıl eẅch gebüre daran beweıſet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_238_r1l4">Jr vns <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex></expan> dankneme <expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_237" id="117v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Eger</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die wir nehst zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> und zum <expan>Ellmpog<ex>en</ex></expan> gesant
            hetten, wol fürbracht und gesagt, wie ir in die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> und auch
            ewr <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> gelihen und zugeschikt und
              <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und guten <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in den
            sachen beweiset habt, des wir <expan>ewer<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiss
                <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> und umb ewch und die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>zu verschulde<ex>n</ex></expan>, wo das an uns gelangt. Denn wo wir
                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> judica.</ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula"><ab>
<pb facs="#facs_238" id="118r"/>
            Cettula <expan>int<ex>er</ex>clusa</expan>: Auch <expan>l<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>, ob ir von den
                  <expan>lawffe<ex>n</ex></expan> zu Beheim icht meͣr hettet, die uns <expan>zu
                  verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> sein, daz ir uns bey <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet, als vil ewch gebüre, daran beweiset ir
              uns <expan>sund<ex>er</ex></expan> dankneme <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex>.</expan>
</ab></div>
</div></body>
